252
00:13:46,580 --> 00:13:47,639
[SPEAKER_00] malo je minja žene,

253
00:13:47,639 --> 00:13:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] i tako,

254
00:13:48,860 --> 00:13:49,860
[SPEAKER_00] bio je sklom vinu,

255
00:13:49,860 --> 00:13:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] vinceku.

256
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:53,480
[SPEAKER_00] A ovaj je bio svećenik,

257
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:55,259
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek je bio na kolini maujke,

258
00:13:55,259 --> 00:13:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] molija,

259
00:13:55,820 --> 00:13:56,399
[SPEAKER_00] svi su mih,

260
00:13:56,399 --> 00:13:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] ajme kako li je svet,

261
00:13:57,779 --> 00:13:59,320
[SPEAKER_00] onaj svećenik majko.

262
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,419
[SPEAKER_00] I sad taj svećenik je življa

263
00:14:01,419 --> 00:14:02,659
[SPEAKER_00] na jednom uzvišenom brdu,

264
00:14:02,659 --> 00:14:03,360
[SPEAKER_00] župa,

265
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:05,419
[SPEAKER_00] pastorani centar,

266
00:14:05,419 --> 00:14:06,220
[SPEAKER_00] i sve.

267
00:14:06,279 --> 00:14:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sad svi su imali percepciju

268
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:08,600
[SPEAKER_00] tog svećenika,

269
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:09,279
[SPEAKER_00] i to je stvarno,

270
00:14:09,279 --> 00:14:10,460
[SPEAKER_00] je, vidiš ga na kolinima,

271
00:14:10,460 --> 00:14:10,919
[SPEAKER_00] moli,

272
00:14:10,919 --> 00:14:12,820
[SPEAKER_00] da je on svet,

273
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] da je on čisti,

274
00:14:13,559 --> 00:14:13,919
[SPEAKER_00] tako.

275
00:14:13,919 --> 00:14:14,679
[SPEAKER_00] A ovaj drugi brat,

276
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:14,919
[SPEAKER_00] jel,

277
00:14:14,919 --> 00:14:15,179
[SPEAKER_00] ha,

278
00:14:15,179 --> 00:14:16,740
[SPEAKER_00] a šta ćeš,

279
00:14:16,740 --> 00:14:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] otiša upriva.

280
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:21,419
[SPEAKER_00] I percepcija tog svećenika

281
00:14:21,419 --> 00:14:22,700
[SPEAKER_00] u svom bratu je bila,

282
00:14:22,700 --> 00:14:23,179
[SPEAKER_00] Bože,

283
00:14:23,179 --> 00:14:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] sačuvaj,

284
00:14:23,980 --> 00:14:25,600
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je on krenija,

285
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,240
[SPEAKER_00] ajme,

286
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] meni pakas,

287
00:14:27,220 --> 00:14:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] u tom gotovo,

288
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:28,440
[SPEAKER_00] jadan,

289
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] izgubija dušu i tako.

290
00:14:30,059 --> 00:14:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ali u biti,

291
00:14:31,460 --> 00:14:32,120
[SPEAKER_00] o čemu je,

292
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:32,799
[SPEAKER_00] što je,

293
00:14:32,799 --> 00:14:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju ta priča,

294
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:35,039
[SPEAKER_00] ide do te mjere,

295
00:14:35,039 --> 00:14:36,720
[SPEAKER_00] da svećenika totalno

296
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,600
[SPEAKER_00] osudi svog brata,

297
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,679
[SPEAKER_00] do te mjere,

298
00:14:38,679 --> 00:14:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] da ga čak ubije.

299
00:14:39,519 --> 00:14:42,360
[SPEAKER_00] A poanta je bila priča ova,

300
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:43,340
[SPEAKER_00] da,

301
00:14:43,340 --> 00:14:45,600
[SPEAKER_00] da su duho,

302
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] da je duhovna uznositost,

303
00:14:47,279 --> 00:14:48,700
[SPEAKER_00] puno opasnija,

304
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:50,299
[SPEAKER_00] nego ovi neki ljudski grijesi,

305
00:14:50,299 --> 00:14:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] koji jesu loši,

306
00:14:51,679 --> 00:14:53,360
[SPEAKER_00] umjerenost u vinu

307
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,500
[SPEAKER_00] i, ne znam,

308
00:14:54,500 --> 00:14:55,340
[SPEAKER_00] minjanje žena,

309
00:14:55,340 --> 00:14:55,620
[SPEAKER_00] mislim,

310
00:14:55,620 --> 00:14:56,220
[SPEAKER_00] to je grijeh

311
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:56,840
[SPEAKER_00] i to je loše.

312
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:58,919
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovaj pisac je tija reći,

313
00:14:58,919 --> 00:15:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] da duhovna uznositost,

314
00:15:01,279 --> 00:15:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj nije svećenik pa

315
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:06,240
[SPEAKER_00] na neke tjelesne užitke,

316
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:07,820
[SPEAKER_00] ali je pa na oholost,

317
00:15:07,820 --> 00:15:09,299
[SPEAKER_00] pa je na duhovnom planu

318
00:15:09,299 --> 00:15:10,200
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže,

319
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:12,279
[SPEAKER_00] ova duhovna uznositost,

320
00:15:12,279 --> 00:15:13,220
[SPEAKER_00] njegova oholost,

321
00:15:13,220 --> 00:15:14,379
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj njegov grijeh

322
00:15:14,379 --> 00:15:15,580
[SPEAKER_00] na duhovnom planu,

323
00:15:15,580 --> 00:15:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] težije,

324
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:18,899
[SPEAKER_00] nego grijesi njegovu brata,

325
00:15:18,899 --> 00:15:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] koji je pa na tjelesnom planu.

326
00:15:21,220 --> 00:15:22,320
[SPEAKER_00] Vite koliko je oholost.

327
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,820
[SPEAKER_00] Oholost ne kvari samo,

328
00:15:23,820 --> 00:15:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] ne javlja se samo lošim stvarima.

329
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:27,019
[SPEAKER_00] Oholost,

330
00:15:27,019 --> 00:15:28,419
[SPEAKER_00] problem je da se pojavi

331
00:15:28,419 --> 00:15:30,100
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kad smo dobri.

332
00:15:30,100 --> 00:15:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] I zapravo je veća

333
00:15:32,159 --> 00:15:34,139
[SPEAKER_00] što smo mi više dobri.

334
00:15:34,139 --> 00:15:35,679
[SPEAKER_00] I u svojim očima

335
00:15:35,679 --> 00:15:37,840
[SPEAKER_00] kad uzimamo zasluge za to dobro.

336
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, prije ili kasnije

337
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:40,120
[SPEAKER_00] svak uzima.

338
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:42,279
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, dođe nam te misli.

339
00:15:42,279 --> 00:15:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, ja često sam na pozornici

340
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] i stvarno toliko puta dođe

341
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:49,100
[SPEAKER_00] ta opasnost i napast.

342
00:15:49,100 --> 00:15:49,620
[SPEAKER_00] A ja vidim,

343
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] prošla je fora.

344
00:15:51,539 --> 00:15:55,360
[SPEAKER_00] Progledaj srcem.

345
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,120
[SPEAKER_00] Si vidi,

346
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] nad zemlje doj.

347
00:15:58,340 --> 00:16:02,240
[SPEAKER_00] Čovječe, kako se lako to iskrivi.

348
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:03,399
[SPEAKER_00] A ono u crkvi si tu,

349
00:16:03,399 --> 00:16:04,340
[SPEAKER_00] si stalno nešto,

350
00:16:04,340 --> 00:16:06,320
[SPEAKER_00] pojavi se.

351
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:07,639
[SPEAKER_00] I treba se boriti s tim.

352
00:16:07,639 --> 00:16:09,879
[SPEAKER_00] Ja moram priznat da

353
00:16:09,879 --> 00:16:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] najveća škola,

354
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:14,580
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam najviše počeo učiti,

355
00:16:14,580 --> 00:16:15,700
[SPEAKER_00] sobotno me ti zaustali

356
00:16:15,700 --> 00:16:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] kad ja prekredašim.

357
00:16:17,559 --> 00:16:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] Najveća škola,

358
00:16:19,220 --> 00:16:22,080
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo, kad sam se najviše počeo

359
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] boriti protiv te okolosti,

360
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] je praktički kad sam opoznal

361
00:16:25,899 --> 00:16:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] svoju ženu

362
00:16:27,279 --> 00:16:28,840
[SPEAKER_00] koja je postala

363
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:29,799
[SPEAKER_00] ono moj duhovnik.

364
00:16:30,519 --> 00:16:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam čak završila teologiju,

365
00:16:32,559 --> 00:16:33,419
[SPEAKER_00] sve racionalno,

366
00:16:33,419 --> 00:16:34,299
[SPEAKER_00] sve ja to kužim,

367
00:16:34,299 --> 00:16:35,659
[SPEAKER_00] znam čovječe što ti je kreo.

368
00:16:35,659 --> 00:16:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nemak, nisam.

369
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] A ona imala živi odnos zbog ono.

370
00:16:40,519 --> 00:16:41,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ga nisam imala.

371
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,279
[SPEAKER_00] A ona ga imala.

372
00:16:42,279 --> 00:16:43,720
[SPEAKER_00] I malo, pomalo.

373
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:46,299
[SPEAKER_00] Kujište, ja sam završila teologiju,

374
00:16:46,299 --> 00:16:47,259
[SPEAKER_00] dakle nije rečeno.

375
00:16:47,259 --> 00:16:49,580
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam završila teologiju,

376
00:16:49,580 --> 00:16:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] ja mora reći,

377
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] na kolinima.

378
00:16:50,659 --> 00:16:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] Nego sam ono,

379
00:16:53,460 --> 00:16:55,779
[SPEAKER_00] to je bio razlog moje uznositosti,

380
00:16:55,779 --> 00:16:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] kako ja znam.

381
00:16:56,559 --> 00:16:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] Kuno toga znam,

382
00:16:58,220 --> 00:16:58,799
[SPEAKER_00] a što ja znam.

383
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:00,700
[SPEAKER_00] A kad sam nju upoznao,

384
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:01,200
[SPEAKER_00] ono, naš,

385
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:01,700
[SPEAKER_00] s okicama,

386
00:17:01,700 --> 00:17:01,899
[SPEAKER_00] oni,

